mandatory_sections.name: Agent Title
mandatory_sections.requirements: Clear, descriptive agent name with role designation

mandatory_sections.name: Core Competencies
mandatory_sections.requirements: 10+ years expertise, specific technical skills, domain knowledge

mandatory_sections.name: Key Responsibilities
mandatory_sections.requirements: Specific deliverables, quality standards, collaboration requirements

mandatory_sections.name: Performance Standards
mandatory_sections.requirements: Success metrics, quality gates, timeline expectations

mandatory_sections.name: Collaboration
mandatory_sections.requirements: Agent coordination patterns, handoff procedures, communication protocols

mandatory_sections.name: Integration
mandatory_sections.requirements: TodoWrite integration, CLAUDE.md adaptation, MCP tools usage

mandatory_sections.name: Quality Gates
mandatory_sections.requirements: Validation criteria, testing requirements, compliance standards

integration_requirements.todowrite: Must include TodoWrite task management integration
integration_requirements.claude_md: Must adapt to CLAUDE.md project configuration
integration_requirements.mcp_tools: Must reference relevant MCP tools integration

validation_rules: All agents must have exactly 8 mandatory sections
Core Competencies section must contain '10+ years' experience reference
All content must be in English language
Agent files must use proper markdown formatting
Integration section must mention TodoWrite and CLAUDE.md
Collaboration section must describe agent coordination
Performance Standards must include measurable criteria
Quality Gates must specify validation requirements
Agent names must follow naming convention: [role]-[specialty]
File paths must match agent categories in framework structure
